    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Distribution>, java.util.Collection<Distribution>, java.util.Set<Distribution>

    public class DistributionSet
extends java.util.LinkedHashSet<Distribution>
    Represents a set of distributions. The order in which distributions are inserted is preserved (but does not affect equality of distributions sets).
